 ever since. It was the name of the central character of  Lewis Carroll's  Alice's Adventures in Wonderland (  1865 ) and Through the Looking Glass (  1872 ), who was based on his child friend  Alice Liddell , daughter of the Dean of Christ Church, Oxford."],"variants":[{"name":"Alys","meanings":["Variant spelling of   Alice ."]},{"name":"Alis","meanings":["equivalent of <b>Alice</b> ."]}]},{"name":"Boleyn","type":"LAST","attribution":"Dictionary of American Family Names © Patrick Hanks 2003, 2006.","meanings":["English (of Norman origin): variant of   Bullen  .","Flemish: derivative of the personal name <i>Bol</i>, from   Baldwin  ."],"variants":[{"name":"Bullen","meanings":["Irish: A name derived from the Irish Cullen signifying whelp."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Alice  Boleyn Bolling was born about 1326, in Otterden, Kent, England, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 son with Henry Aucher."},"et":{"abt 1326–":"umbes 1326–Surnud","1335–1400":"1335–1400","1352–Male":"1352–Surnud","1326–Female":"1326–Surnud","1326":"1326","abt 1326":"umbes 1326","1335":"1335","1400":"1400","1352":"1352","abt 1352":"umbes 1352","Otterden, Kent, Eng.":"Otterden, Kent, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Otterden, Kent, Eng":"Otterden, Kent, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"abt 1326–":"noin 1326–Kuollut","1335–1400":"1335–1400","1352–Male":"1352–Kuollut","1326–Female":"1326–Kuollut","1326":"1326","abt 1326":"noin 1326","1335":"1335","1400":"1400","1352":"1352","abt 1352":"noin 1352","Otterden, Kent, Eng.":"Otterden, Kent, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Otterden, Kent, Eng":"Otterden, Kent, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"abt 1326–":"environ 1326–Décédée","1335–1400":"1335–1400","1352–Male":"1352–Décédé","1326–Female":"1326–Décédée","1326":"1326","abt 1326":"environ 1326","1335":"1335","1400":"1400","1352":"1352","abt 1352":"environ 1352","Otterden, Kent, Eng.":"Otterden, Kent, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Otterden, Kent, Eng":"Otterden, Kent, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Al